
QUICK INSTALL:

    $ ./configure
    $ make
 
   Or, you can just do make
    $ make


  You need sqlite3 if you want to compile all the programs. However
  this should still compile without sqlite3.

     $ wget http://www.sqlite.org/sqlite-3.2.1.tar.gz
     $ tar -xzf sqlite-3.2.1.tar.gz
     $ cd sqlite-3.2.1
     $ ./configure
     $ make
     $ su -
     $ make install


      



